item.description:
I've decided that the traffic will be take too much time from climbing and there will be another weekend to go up that way that will not be packed with bikers and visitors to the bike week events.  They will be traveling on the exact roads we would be to get there. 

If you are still interested in meeting to climb Stonehouse let me know, or if you prefer to try out Rines hill then go REALLY early! 

Please let me know if you are changing your response.

If you need gear let me know,

Kellie
item.name: Climb Stonehouse Pond
